<header>
    <div class="header-overlay"></div>
    <div class="header-content">
        <div class="header-content-inner">
<!--                 <h1 style="font-size: 2em">Campus Perks</h1> -->
            <p class="subtitle-phrase">A community for more than just tutoring</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl page-scroll text-color">Get In Touch</a>
            <br>
            <a href="#about" class="btn btn-circle page-scroll">
            <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down animated"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

</div>
</header>

<section class="bg-primary" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-heading">How It Works</h2>
                <hr class="light">
                <p class="p-questions">Want to get an on-demand, on-campus tutoring session a few hours right before your exam?</p>
                <p class="p-questions">Struggling to find past exams?</p>
                <p class="p-questions">Want to get deeper insight from your peers on your professors exams and assignments?</p>
                <p class="p-questions">Feel like meeting new people and donâ€™t know where?</p>
                <p class="text-faded">Campus Perks aims to serve as a community enhancer, bringing students closer together. We want to help you be more efficient, boost your learning experience on campus  and save more money. We think you should be entitled to the following perks:</p>
            </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <%= image_tag "Tutoring.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
                <h3>Peer Tutoring Perk</h3>
                    <p class="text-faded">Get tutored by students who took the same class and professor a semester ago. Get insights on their exams and homework, all while getting to know your peers better. Make a quick buck by teaching fellow peers during those long hours between classes and schedule appointments at your own convenience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <%= image_tag "NoteShare.png", class: "img-responsive" %>

                <h3>NoteShare Perk</h3>
                    <p class="text-faded">Take a snap of past exams, homework solutions and papers, and post it on Campus Perks helping out your peers. Like, share and comment on their notes and learn from them through the comments section.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <%= image_tag "Events.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
                <h3>On-Campus Events Perk</h3>
                    <p class="text-faded">Create and invite your peers to join your On-Campus events. Attend other events that are posted and get to know like-minded individuals.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div><!--close container-->
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-heading">Sign Up Today</h2>
                <h3>Tell us why you're ready for the final frontier.</h3>
                <hr class="primary">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
              <%= simple_form_for @visitor do |f| %>
                <%= f.error_notification %>
                <%= f.input :full_name, label: false, :placeholder => 'Your name...' %>
                <%= f.input :campus_name, label: false, :placeholder => 'Your campus name...' %>
                <%= f.input :email, label: false, :placeholder => 'Your email address...' %>
                <br/>
                <%= f.button :submit, "Subscribe", :class => "submit" %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<aside class="bg-dark">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="call-to-action">
            <p class="footer-title">Copyright 2015 Campus Perks</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</aside>

